**Ghost Election** | Poll
Available Options: @Ghostly, Abstain
Allowed Voters: @Ghostly
Passive Start Night: [Temporal: Night 2+, Condition: @Ghostly exists]
  • (@(AttrRole:Revenant,Ghostly:True) exists) and (@(AttrRole:Poltergeist,Ghostly:True) exists) and (not (@(AttrRole:Banshee,Ghostly:True) exists)):
    ‣ Target `Banshee` (Role)
    ‣ Create Poll in #graveyard_votes as `Banshee Election`
  • (@(AttrRole:Revenant,Ghostly:True) exists) and (not (@(AttrRole:Poltergeist,Ghostly:True) exists)):
    ‣ Target `Poltergeist` (Role)
    ‣ Create Poll in #graveyard_votes as `Poltergeist Election`
  • not (@(AttrRole:Revenant,Ghostly:True) exists):
    ‣ Target `Revenant` (Role)
    ‣ Create Poll in #graveyard_votes as `Revenant Election`
On Poll Closed:
  • Grant @Target to @Winner 
  • Announce `@Winner was elected as @Target[role]`
